<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 12:20:59 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>莫迪领导的印度人民党在与中国接壤的阿鲁纳恰尔邦保留权力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/modis-bjp-retains-power-indian-state-bordering-china-2024-06-02/</link><description>官员和政界人士周日表示，印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的印度人民党赢得了与中国接壤的阿鲁纳恰尔邦的地区选举，而当地一个政党则在喜马拉雅山锡金邦赢得了权力。</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 11:16:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/modis-bjp-retains-power-indian-state-bordering-china-2024-06-02/</guid></item><item><title>伊朗外交部就海湾群岛问题召见中国驻德黑兰大使</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/irans-foreign-ministry-summons-chinese-ambassador-tehran-over-gulf-islands-2024-06-02/</link><description>据伊朗官方媒体周日报道，伊朗外交部已召见中国驻德黑兰大使，抗议中国与阿联酋就伊朗对阿联酋也声称拥有主权的三个岛屿的主权发表的声明。</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 10:49:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/irans-foreign-ministry-summons-chinese-ambassador-tehran-over-gulf-islands-2024-06-02/</guid></item><item><title>唐纳德·特朗普加入了他曾试图禁止的 TikTok 视频平台</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/donald-trump-joins-tiktok-video-platform-he-once-sought-ban-2024-06-02/</link><description>共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普加入了 TikTok，这是中国科技巨头字节跳动旗下的短视频社交媒体平台，他在担任总统期间曾试图在 11 月美国大选前禁止该平台。</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 08:08:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/donald-trump-joins-tiktok-video-platform-he-once-sought-ban-2024-06-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国称菲律宾人员在争议海域用枪指着中国海警</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-philippine-personnel-pointed-guns-chinese-coast-guard-disputed-waters-2024-06-02/</link><description>中国官方媒体周日称，上个月，一艘菲律宾船只上的人员在南海争议海域用枪指着中国海警。</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 07:32:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-philippine-personnel-pointed-guns-chinese-coast-guard-disputed-waters-2024-06-02/</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰泽伦斯基主导亚洲安全会议，中国和台湾贸易倒刺</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/ukraines-zelenskiy-dominates-asia-security-conference-china-taiwan-trade-barbs-2024-06-02/</link><description>在中国国防部长猛烈抨击台湾的“分裂分子”后，乌克兰总统意外出席了亚洲最大的安全会议，引发了台北的强烈回应。</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 06:43:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/ukraines-zelenskiy-dominates-asia-security-conference-china-taiwan-trade-barbs-2024-06-02/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚寻求与中国进行军事会谈并与菲律宾建立关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-seeks-military-talks-with-china-ties-with-philippines-2024-06-02/</link><description>副总理理查德·马勒斯周日在香格里拉对话安全峰会上表示，澳大利亚已要求与中国进行军事会谈，并愿意与菲律宾走得更近。</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 05:36:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-seeks-military-talks-with-china-ties-with-philippines-2024-06-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国和阿联酋准备交换国防和安全经验</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-uae-ready-trade-defence-security-experiences-2024-06-02/</link><description>中国外交部周日表示，中国和阿拉伯联合酋长国强调愿意交流防务安全经验，以提升两国军事人员和安全机构的能力。</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 04:45:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-uae-ready-trade-defence-security-experiences-2024-06-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国称与台湾和平“统一”的前景受到“侵蚀”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/prospect-peaceful-reunification-with-taiwan-being-eroded-china-says-2024-06-02/</link><description>中国国防部长董军周日表示，与台湾和平“统一”的前景正日益受到台独势力和外部势力的“侵蚀”，此举引起了台北政府的愤怒回应。</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 01:46:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/prospect-peaceful-reunification-with-taiwan-being-eroded-china-says-2024-06-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国国防部长泽连斯基主导香格里拉对话会最后一天</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinese-defence-minister-ukraines-zelenskiy-dominate-shangri-la-dialogues-last-2024-06-02/</link><description>在中国国防部长董军发表讲话的前一天，美国国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀告诉代表们，印太地区仍然是美国的一个重点关注点。</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 00:16:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinese-defence-minister-ukraines-zelenskiy-dominate-shangri-la-dialogues-last-2024-06-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国在历史性的样本回收任务中登陆月球背面</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/china-lands-uncrewed-spacecraft-far-side-moon-2024-06-01/</link><description>此次登陆提升了中国在全球登月热潮中的太空强国地位，各国都希望利用月球矿物来维持长期的宇航员任务和月球基地。</description><pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 23:45:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/china-lands-uncrewed-spacecraft-far-side-moon-2024-06-01/</guid></item><item><title>摩尔多瓦反对派领导人呼吁与俄罗斯和中国建立更好的关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/moldovan-opposition-leader-calls-better-ties-with-russia-china-2024-06-01/</link><description>摩尔多瓦最大反对党的亲俄罗斯领导人呼吁改善与俄罗斯和中国的关系，并敦促其他团体联合起来，在十月的选举中选出亲欧洲总统马亚·桑杜的单一挑战者。</description><pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 17:42:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/moldovan-opposition-leader-calls-better-ties-with-russia-china-2024-06-01/</guid></item><item><title>加拿大国防部长表示，加拿大向中国提出了外国干涉的担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/canada-raised-foreign-interference-concerns-with-china-defence-minister-says-2024-06-01/</link><description>加拿大国防部长周六表示，在一次罕见的两国国防部长会议上，加拿大警告中国不要干预其选举。</description><pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 08:37:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/canada-raised-foreign-interference-concerns-with-china-defence-minister-says-2024-06-01/</guid></item><item><title>调查显示5月份中国新建住宅价格连续第9个月上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-new-home-prices-inch-up-9th-month-may-survey-shows-2024-06-01/</link><description>一项私人调查显示，中国新房价格在 5 月份连续第九个月小幅上涨，受到一系列支撑中国受危机打击的房地产行业的支持性措施的推动。</description><pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 02:40:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-new-home-prices-inch-up-9th-month-may-survey-shows-2024-06-01/</guid></item><item><title>美国将焦点转向中国风险 泽伦斯基抵达亚洲防务会议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-defense-chief-refocuses-attention-china-security-risks-2024-06-01/</link><description>人们越来越担心，华盛顿专注于帮助乌克兰对抗俄罗斯的入侵和支持以色列在加沙的战争，从而转移了印度-太平洋地区的注意力。</description><pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 01:10:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-defense-chief-refocuses-attention-china-security-risks-2024-06-01/</guid></item><item><title>中国粮食安全法生效 力争绝对自给自足</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-food-security-law-comes-into-force-aims-absolute-self-sufficiency-2024-05-31/</link><description>中国首部旨在实现主粮“绝对自给自足”的粮食安全法于周六生效，加强了全球最大农产品进口国降低对海外采购依赖的努力。</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 23:02:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-food-security-law-comes-into-force-aims-absolute-self-sufficiency-2024-05-31/</guid></item></channel></rss>